  h4 class="pb-2 text-lg font-bold text-left underline"
    ' How We Use and Share the Information
  p class="pb-4"
    ' We use Personal Information and Other Information to provide you Services, process your donations, solicit your feedback, inform you about our services, personalize communications and fundraising appeals that we believe will be of interest to you, and to improve our Services to you. We do not sell user information.
  p class="pb-4"
    ' We may also use and/or share Personal Information, Other Information, and User Content as described below:
  ol class="pl-10 list-disc"
