    li class="pb-2"
      ' We may employ other companies and individuals to perform functions on our behalf. Examples may include providing technical assistance and customer service. These other companies will have access to Personal Information and Other Information only as necessary to perform their functions in connection with our Services and to the extent permitted by law.
    li class="pb-2"
      ' In an ongoing effort to better understand visitors to our site and our products and services, we may analyze Other Information in aggregate form in order to operate, maintain, manage, and improve our services. This aggregate information does not identify individuals personally. We may share this aggregate data with our affiliates, agents, and business partners. We may also disclose aggregated user statistics in order to describe our services to current and prospective business partners and to other third parties for other lawful purposes.
    li class="pb-2"
      ' We may share some or all of the Personal Information and Other Information with any of our subsidiaries or other companies under common control with us.
    li class="pb-2"
      ' We may use nonprofit logos, marks, name, mission statement, vision, services information, EIN number, NTEE codes, address, contact information, website, email, phone number, populations served, cause categories, keyword tags, social media links, hours of operation, location information or other identifiers provided by a Nonprofit Representative User when updating a Nonprofit Profile on the Giving Connection Website to continue the normal course of Giving Connection business.
    li class="pb-2"
      ' To the extent permitted by law, we may also disclose Personal Information and Other Information: (i) when required by law, or judicial or governmental  order; or (ii) whenever we reasonably believe that disclosing such information is necessary or advisable, for example, to protect the rights, property, or safety of Giving Connection, our Users or others.
  h4 class="pb-2 text-lg font-bold text-left underline"
    ' Accessing and Modifying Information and Communication Preferences
  p class="pb-4"
